&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The
Development hereby permitted shall only be carried out and completed strictly
