approval of details.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;



&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &amp;quot;PT Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;REASON: To ensure that the development hereby permitted is carried
